title: The New Slow Cooker Cookbook (2016) (Epub) Gooner
description:
The New Slow Cooker Cookbook - More than 200 Modern, Healthy and Easy Recipes for the Classic Cooker (2016) (Epub) Gooner

Publisher: Adams Media Corporation; 1 edition (29 Jan. 2016)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1440594112
ISBN-13: 978-1440594113

A modern twist on classic slow cooker recipes!Forget grandma's slow-cooker recipes! With this cookbook, you'll whip up hundreds of healthy dishes that will satisfy everyone's tastebuds. Featuring more than 200 delicious slow cooker recipes, you'll learn how easy it is to use the classic appliance to create modern, nutritious meals from scratch.
